briefdescription.para: Init TO configuration and dump tables for a channel.

simplesect.title: Description
simplesect.para: This function initializes the two tables for a channel

simplesect.title: Assumptions, External Events, and Notes:
simplesect.para: This function should be called only once per channel.

parameterdescription.para: A TO_ChannelData_t pointer that references the channel data structure

simplesect.title: Description
simplesect.para: This function validates TO's Configuration table

parameterdescription.para: Pointer to config table data from cFE table services

detaileddescription.para: If unsuccessful, TO_CONFIG_TABLE_RETURN_INVALID_VERSION, TO_CONFIG_TABLE_RETURN_NO_SECONDARY_HEADER, TO_CONFIG_TABLE_MSG_FLOW_MSG_LIMIT_ERR, TO_CONFIG_TABLE_MSG_FLOW_PQ_ID_ERR, TO_CONFIG_TABLE_NULL_PTR_ERR, TO_CONFIG_TABLE_PQUEUE_STATE_ERR, TO_CONFIG_TABLE_PQUEUE_QTYPE_ERR, TO_CONFIG_TABLE_PQUEUE_MSG_LIMIT_ERR TO_CONFIG_TABLE_NO_PQUEUES_ERR, TO_CONFIG_TABLE_MSG_FLOW_FILTER_ERR, TO_CONFIG_TABLE_QUEUE_ERR, #TO_CONFIG_TABLE_ANOMALY_BUFFER_ERR.

simplesect.para: This function manages the config table and obtains a pointer to its data.

simplesect.title: Description
simplesect.para: This function processes TO's new Config table and set Config parameters with new values.

briefdescription.para: Intermediate function to add a TO table type to allow table validation per channel type (Ground, Onboard, Storage) This function is used to help validate the Ground channel table.

simplesect.title: Description
simplesect.para: This function add channel type to be pass to validation function.

parameterdescription.para: Pointer to config table data from cFE table services

briefdescription.para: This manages all the tables in the app.

simplesect.title: Description
simplesect.para: This function performs the table management for each channel's dump and configuration tables with cFE table services.

simplesect.title: Assumptions, External Events, and Notes:
simplesect.para: All tables have been initialized via TO_InitCoinfigTbl(). This is called during app cyclic operations.

briefdescription.para: This manages all the tables for a given channel.

simplesect.title: Description
simplesect.para: This function performs the table management for a channel's dump and configuration tables with cFE table services.

simplesect.title: Assumptions, External Events, and Notes:
simplesect.para: All channel tables have been initialized via TO_InitCoinfigTbl().

parameterdescription.para: T=this is the first time to call this function at app initialization, F=this is being called in the app main loop
The index of the channel to manage

simplesect.title: Description
simplesect.para: This function loads the built-in emergency backup TO config table. For use when the config table can't be provided by cFE TBL, such as the config file can't be read from the filesystem.

parameterdescription.para: A TO_ChannelData_t pointer that references the channel data structure
